ulife.co.nz/attachment/article/2018-07-24/ulife-sixberral-02.png\" style=\"width: 100%;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-1\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--end of row for 品牌故事-->\r\n\r\n<div style=\"padding:40px 0;\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:36px;\">品牌文化</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">_____</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row\"><!--row品牌文件内容-->\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-1\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-10\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">以一个崇高的使命来动摇一个平坦的软饮料市场与实验味道和一个新的质量水平。</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">SLOGAN</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">&lt; 为您带来健康美味的产品！&gt;</span></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">我们用心制造出品质卓越的产品。所有护肤品都是将传统的毛利护肤疗法、新西兰丰富的天然植物资源和现代工业技术的完美结合。我们的麦卢卡蜂蜜只采用单一麦卢卡花蜜为原料，保持着最原生态的纯净活性与健康。希望您能体验到我们无与伦比的优秀产品。</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-1\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--end of row品牌文件内容-->\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row\" sytle=\"padding:40px 0;\"><!--品牌文化图片-->\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-1\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-10\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-4\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://ulife.co.nz/attachment/article/2018-07-24/ulife-sixberral-03.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-4\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://ulife.co.nz/attachment/article/2018-07-24/ulife-sixberral-04.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-4\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://ulife.co.nz/attachment/article/2018-07-24/ulife-sixberral-05.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-1\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-1\">&nbsp;</d